channel.title: SourceForge.net: SF.net Project News: acx100 - Wireless chipset Linux driver
channel.description: SF.net Project News: acx100 - Wireless chipset Linux driver (acx100 project) - Open Source Linux driver for wireless network cards (DWL-520+ PCI, DWL-650+ CardBus, GL-2422MP mini-PCI etc.) that are based on the entirely undocumented Texas Instruments ACX100 chip, for modern kernel versions (2.4.x - 2.6.x). BSD support planned.
